Package: punKEGGer
Title: Parse, Expand, Annotate and Visualize KEGG Pathway Networks
Version: 0.99.4
Authors@R: c(
    person("Guillermo", "de Anda Jáuregui",
           email = "gdeanda@inmegen.edu.mx",
           role = c("aut","cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2551-3059"))
)
Description: Provides tools to parse KEGG pathway KGML files into tidy graphs,
    expand metanodes (e.g., multi-gene entries), annotate them with custom
    dictionaries, and produce consistent visualizations using ggraph.
    Enables integration of KEGG pathways with tidygraph-based workflows.
